headline: Wells Fargo upgrades Celanese on better earnings prospect
summary: Investing.com -- Wells Fargo upgraded Celanese (NYSE:CE) Corp to Overweight. While it lowered earnings forecasts for Dow Inc (NYSE:DOW) and LyondellBasell Industries (NYSE:LYB) amid continued near-term weakness in commodity chemicals. Though analysts say there a possible inflection point in the second half of the year.
